metatags.og:description: A video of a woman shooting a gun has been viewed millions of times on Twitter alongside an English-language claim that the woman is Swedish climate activist Greta Thunberg. The claim is false; the footage actually shows a Swedish engineer, who confirmed with Brazilian media she was the one featured in the video, which she posted on Twitter before it went viral on social media.
